 * @brief          : Main program body - Temperature Monitoring Board 2026 MK1
 *                   Optimized for 30Hz scan rate across all 24 sensors
 *
 * Pin Mapping:
 *   PA2  - ADC1_IN2  (MUX_FILT_OUT - filtered analog input)
 *   PA5  - SPI1_SCK  (SCLK to all ADG731 multiplexers)
 *   PA7  - SPI1_MOSI (DIN  to all ADG731 multiplexers)
 *   PB0  - SYNC1     (Chip select for U201 - MUX 0)
 *   PB1  - SYNC2     (Chip select for U203 - MUX 1)
 *   PB2  - SYNC3     (Chip select for U202 - MUX 2)
 *   PA11 - CAN_RX
 *   PA12 - CAN_TX
